comment: Butler's (CHI) contact does not affect Oladipo's (ORL) shot.
Vucevic (ORL) makes contact with Gasol's (CHI) arm and the contact affects his shot.
Gordon (ORL) enters the paint area prior to the free throw being released.
Gordon's (ORL) contact does not affect Brooks' (CHI) shot.
Gasol (CHI) does not dislodge Vucevic (ORL) on the rebound attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Vucevic (ORL) was the last player to touch the ball before it went OOB was upheld and CHI was awarded possession.
Vucevic (ORL) bumps Gasol (CHI) and affects his RSBQ.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Gasol (CHI) was the last player to touch the ball before it went OOB was upheld and ORL was awarded possession.
Noah (CHI) commits a take foul on Oladipo (ORL).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the officials determined that the take foul was committed with :00.4 seconds remaining.
